node.text: Pre-Sale 50% off 🚨 I’ve had requests for 10 drawer cart labels for a long time and I decided to tackle that project this summer. I picked up a couple of carts to work with and I’m in love with how they both turned out! I’m leaving this pre-sale discount on until the set is complete. It should be done tonight or tomorrow morning! Link in profile- https://bit.ly/teachercartlabels

node.text:
Look at all these goodies I just found at @michaelsstores! #ad I always had my students make a self portrait at the beginning of the year, but how fun would it be for them to create their own little person that represents them?

I love how their new foam shape people include a variety of skin tones so that children can make a person that looks like them!

You can find everything you need to create these at @michaelsstores 😍
#MakeItWithMichaels

Taking self portraits up a notch! #ad I was at @michaelsstores recently and found these amazing new Creatology foam shape people that I knew would be the perfect back-to-school project!

I love that there's such a great variety of skin tones included, which will make it easy for children to create their own little person that looks just like them! Just hand your students some materials and let their creativity shine!

You can find everything you need for this project at @michaelsstores.

Did you know that teachers can save 15% on their entire purchase year round? Just show your badge and you're good to go!

Link in profile to shop: https://bit.ly/36KYdYx

#MakeItWithMichaels
#MichaelsTeacher
